| Multiple datoms same entity | unique_entity_ids deduplicates. entity_lookup returns first datom position. |
| Entity absent | MPH lookup returns None or wrong index → verify fails → return None. |
| OnceLock concurrent init | get_or_init synchronized. Safe. |

